## What It Does NOT Do

- ❌ Does **not** create effects (effects are separate modules)
- ❌ Does **not** handle audio analysis (uses P1-A1 + P1-A2)
- ❌ Does **not** manage effect lifecycle (use EffectManager)
- ❌ Does **not** provide visual rendering (use Renderer)
- ❌ Does **not** handle MIDI input (use MIDIController)
- ❌ Does **not** store effect states (use StateManager)

