## Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| Performance degradation with many effects | Medium | High | Frame skipping, effect prioritization |
| Parameter conflicts between effects | Medium | Medium | Effect coordination, parameter namespaces |
| Audio latency affecting reactivity | Low | Medium | Buffer management, real-time priority |
| Memory leaks from effect registration | Low | Medium | Reference counting, cleanup on unregister |
| Thread safety issues | Low | High | Lock-free design, atomic operations |

